window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Within the Tower awaits the Bloodskin Dynasty.</b><br> <br> A group of bosses found throughout its various floors; they share one goal—to wipe out humanity. The end approaches. As John Mavren climbs ever higher up the Tower, he’ll learn that these monsters are not merely challenges to overcome, but may hold the fate of humanity itself in their hands.<br> <br> With the threat of the Twin Dragons heading straight toward the Tower, John embarks on a race against time to stop the calamity. The answers will take him to the peak of the Tower, to the depths of Earth's dungeons, and even forgotten corners of battlegrounds, nothing will stop his quest for the trust, and the power to change the ending.<br> <br> His one final chance to bring the Tower crumbling to the ground, and to free humanity once and for all.<br> <br> <b>From best-seller Wolfe Locke comes b</b><b><i>ook three</i></b><b> in the </b><b><i>Realm Grinder Series</i></b><b>, a Tower Climbing LitRPG about an apocalypse, a Tower of Realms, and a Hero going from strong to stronger.</b></p>"; 
